<br>
Oh, yea some &quot;Dip stick&quot; phoned in to say in effect free information about nuclear space technology should stop and be classified. <br>
<br>
I was gonna say that astronauts, cosmonauts don't risk or lose their lives to go into space for nothing, they expect that the rest of us support space exploration and advance the cause of space and that goes for space tourists too. I mean show me a terrorist or terrorist nation interested in nuke space development to go to Mars or anywhere else in the solar system...they could give-a-sh*t. There's a big difference between what people do to advance peaceful safe exploration of space and a bunch of illegal terrorist bent on production of WMD stuff to kill people with. I mean... isn't  why half the world is at the UN trying to put the cuffs on terrorist and their nations to stop illegal WMD's? I was gonna plug NS website but my Mom wanted me to paint the kitchen...sorry , next time.<br>
<br>
